verbose_text: HeT-A expression in vas-null ovaries expressing constructs that delete part of this region (egfp-vas Delta3-139 or egfp-vas Delta94-127) was highly variable from experiment to experiment, ranging from near wild-type levels to levels similar to vas Delta3-200, and because of this variability the difference from egfp-vas + was not statistically significant (supplementary material Table S1).
